This map is CRAZY, the textures are so weird it makes that map feel like its got so many sides and corners to it, its actually a rectangle but you wouldnt believe it, it has 56 AWP Sniper Rifles and ALOT of hidden places. The Screenshots on this dont really show up that well because the textures make it kind of hard to see. I suggest taking a look for yourself.

It can hold a max of 40 players.
